===more:<P>Discuss the following 2 proposals. Use the Food Facts sheet listed under "Homework 4. Food Discussion" on the Bio 123 homepage to help formulate your response. <P>

Proposal 1. We (the U.S. government) should give away surplus grain to those countries that can't afford to buy it from us. <P>

Proposal 2. We should all become vegetarians to help feed the hungry people of the world and reduce the environmental impact of livestock production. 

